message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with Visual Question Answering (VQA), which involves evaluating a system's visual understanding through its answers to natural language questions about images. This task is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses various models and evaluations, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
